headline: CPC Launches Industry-First Product for Cell and Gene Therapy Sterile Processing
summary: CPC (Colder Products Company), part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading manufacturer of connection technologies used in biopharmaceutical processing, today announced the launch of its new MicroCNX® Nano Series aseptic connectors, designed to significantly simplify cell and gene therapy (CGT) closed sterile processing.
